{"tid":774024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無出汗係無臭味既巴打分享下生活習慣","createTime":"2018-08-10T04:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T08:11:24.000Z","uid":60313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88029b2f191b796bb0d268cdb1e07f9936e88ea6","tid":774024,"uid":60313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:06:22.000Z","msg":"係咪有部分人天生基因出汗無乜味（唔臭）<br />\n平時食野都係好清？主要係唔酸唔辣，唔食重口味野<br />\n著衫係咪cotton 或者 運動透氣快乾tee 可以大大減少臭味？"},{"pid":"11f7d23b855c40d1e0ea0da5e761c322e7ab2afb","tid":774024,"uid":38017,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82d2037d08ba3b6e76384f36ed81a51306d2c019","tid":774024,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"瘋狂飲水"},{"pid":"eea45af5503a29ac21dfcc39dde5e0ce2c94bcd6","tid":774024,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T04:15:39.000Z","msg":"天生"},{"pid":"c0f57cbadc091461d03bb1a15ec29a79f01f3d01","tid":774024,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:04:53.000Z","msg":"本身出汗真係冇味，由細到大都係<br />\n<br />\n不過少食油脂，多飲水份會好啲"},{"pid":"aeea45d373250026e4a3b62e5460f53f9aedfbc4","tid":774024,"uid":13017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"飲多啲水 食多啲菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3274ab5f9226894e1db07c68279bbe18f77c8b","tid":774024,"uid":60313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"飲多d 水 好似無乜分別<br />\n有d人食完越南野陣味仲勁"},{"pid":"8980e797b2488675ea350b4b72ed4b85e75306bc","tid":774024,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"唔知 天生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  飲食無乜特別話戒口<br />\n<br />\n利申:無味"},{"pid":"c84eb30580bbf0c129ad44667f346478d466a662","tid":774024,"uid":10639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己無臭味係天生<br />\n不過算飲得多水，好少食辣，亦唔鍾意食濃味野"},{"pid":"55792390a9cec97be8e46b610a9b73834ffb51bd","tid":774024,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"出汗實會臭，不過用開止汗劑， 唔香都唔會臭。仲有唔好夾香水/古龍水， 臭得更勁！"},{"pid":"03529fc23eac7d67b4542461a54fbe6f8a43dbf5","tid":774024,"uid":143260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:02:14.000Z","msg":"講真，無汗臭味主要一成係個生活習慣良好，三成靠基因，六成靠個樣，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072aa49bc36bd0a6d917c4b77735c9c4b5a5a205","tid":774024,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"0炸嘢冇味，屎都冇味<br />\n十日唔沖涼冇人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申，食齋十幾年"},{"pid":"5a84cc2560b4f48e5db90ee9445611c934717e75","tid":774024,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c84eb30580bbf0c129ad44667f346478d466a662","tid":774024,"uid":10639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己無臭味係天生<br />\n不過算飲得多水，好少食辣，亦唔鍾意食濃味野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"改到㗎，我以前係燥熱底而家係極寒底"}]}